Subscriber
- start: try to bind a port (return false when not possible to bind a port?)
- stop: unbinds port
- receive(): blocking call to read next message

Publisher
- start: blocking connect to a port
- stop: stop publishing
- send(): sends a message

ServiceReplyer (??)
Message
-> getType()
-> getString()
-> getInputStream()
-> getOutputStream()    
-> clear()


